---
// Dream Wedding FAQ Section
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-background">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-[42px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-4">Common Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">Everything you need to know about planning your dream destination wedding.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 group">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary">Can you help us choose a destination?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed">Absolutely. Our specialists know our destinations inside out. We'll discuss your preferred climate, travel time, budget, and legal requirements to help you find the perfect corner of the world.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 group">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary">Do you offer all-inclusive wedding packages?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed">Yes, many of our resort partners in the Caribbean and Mexico offer exceptional all-inclusive packages that cover everything from the ceremony and flowers to dinner and drinks for your entire guest list.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 group">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary">How does pricing work?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed">We pride ourselves on transparency. Our venue prices are "from" prices based on typical wedding setups. During your consultation, we'll provide a detailed quote based on your specific requirements and guest count.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 group">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary">Can you plan same-sex weddings?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed">Yes, we work with a vast range of inclusive venues in destinations like Mexico, Greece, and Bali that warmly welcome and celebrate same-sex couples. We can also advise on the legal vs. symbolic ceremony options in each location.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 group">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary">How quickly can we book?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed">Some couples book 2 years in advance to secure specific dates, while others plan within 6 months. As soon as you've found your venue through our search, we can begin the booking process immediately.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>